sql_query.sql: SELECT "reports"."id", "reports"."status_ids", "reports"."comment", "reports"."created_at", "reports"."updated_at", "reports"."account_id", "reports"."action_taken_by_account_id", "reports"."target_account_id", "reports"."assigned_account_id", "reports"."uri", "reports"."forwarded", "reports"."category", "reports"."action_taken_at", "reports"."rule_ids" FROM "reports" WHERE "reports"."target_account_id" = $1 AND "reports"."action_taken_at" IS NULL
